[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # add 60 min observation"). The optimizer handles variable durations through
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # the predicted_duration field on each scheduling request.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     104[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
