[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     882[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Run the complete chemotherapy scheduling pipeline for a target date.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     883[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     884[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Steps:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     885[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     1. Build scheduling requests (from EHR orders + duration predictions)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     886[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     2. Build resource model (chairs, nurses, pharmacy capacity)
