[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     889[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     5. Store the schedule to DynamoDB
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     890[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     6. Print the final schedule for review
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     891[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     892[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     In production, this runs as a Step Functions workflow triggered nightly
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     893[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     by an EventBridge scheduled rule. Each step is a separate Lambda function
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     894[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     with error handling and retry logic.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     895[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
